Summary: two white spheres rotating around each other
divs: Sighting DetailsI saw this off my back porch today. I thought it might be a couple of balloons, and it might be, but the thing stayed in the exact same spot for about twenty minutes before moving north. Sorry for the shaky camera, it's tough to focus when you're zooming that far and I didn't have a tripod. No sound, so I didn't record any.
